resources.string: "Released in Oct. 2013, Espresso is the official GUI testing framework for Android.It is intended to test a single application but can also be used to test across applications. Write below a review of this framework!"

Released in Sept. 2017, Kakao is an DSL testing language developed from Espresso. With a more clear syntaxt and easier commands, it fully supports Kotlin. As the same for Espresso, write here below a lovely review for Kakao!
